            "body": "@PixelPirate \n1. It is real newline or just wrap?\n2. You should not be using localized paths, just set `LANG=C` before running Neovim.\n3. `export TMPFILE=\"$(mktmp)\" ; bash -c 'exec -c -a \"\" env -i TMPFILE=\"$TMPFILE\" nvim --cmd \"call writefile([\\$VIM, \\\"\\\"], \\$TMPFILE, \\\"b\\\")\" --cmd qall'` should get you fallback for $VIM in $TMPFILE.\n",
